getCharacterIndex

public int getCharacterIndex(char character)
Returns the character index from the permitted alphabet. Either this index is the default character index from the international register or it is the canonical sorted index of the character in the alphabet.

Parameters:
character - the character whose index should be returned
Returns:
the index of the given character
